
Typical things that need to be changed to make a mac usable.
TODO: figure out how to change these setting without the gui

sp == system preferences

turn off sounds: sp/sound
enable sticky keys: sp/accessibility
remap keys: option <-> control: sp/keyboard, push "modifier keys" in lower right
	(this will make option-arrow change desktops)  Note: option is labeled "alt/option"
hot corners: sp/"desktop & screen saver", push "Hot corners" button in lower right
